article.author: Christopher Palmeri
article.title: Wynn Resorts CEO Said to Weigh Sale of Boston-Area Casino
article.description: Wynn Resorts Ltd.’s new Chief Executive Officer Matt Maddox has had informal talks about a sale of the company’s still-under-construction Massachusetts casino, according to a person familiar with the discussions.
